INSERT INTO `news` (`id`, `title`, `description`, `short_description`, `image`, `added_on`, `slug`) VALUES
(2, 'The Future of E-commerce ', '<p><strong>Live stream shopping is much more than online shopping. Before going into any details, let&rsquo;s have a brief look over what makes Live stream shopping more and more trendy?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first thing you might need to know is the actual concept of Live stream shopping. Many of us considered it as video marketing but it is not that!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Clarify your concept first!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the year 2020, because of the global pandemic, people were tended to stay at their homes. In such scenarios, e-commerce reached the climax. But with a more and more competitive market, it is not enough to just have an eCommerce website. The more reliable you look, the more your business will expand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If one wants to gain the trust of its customers, he should just go to make it done. One way of achieving trust and reliability is to opt for live stream shopping. It covers all the live details with its customers. From minor details to a product review, from unboxing to feature description, and from ambiguities to prompt replies, live streaming caters to all the drawbacks and confusions that customers may have.&nbsp; These features with the live chat fluency to ask any query will make it easy and even easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>We are bringing the very first live stream shopping mall in Pakistan.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Z Mall-The one for all your needs!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Z Mall, all your necessities will be facilitated under one shelter for your ease and comfort. Either it&#39;s men&#39;s fashion or women&#39;s fashion, Z Mall will keep you updated with the latest fashion trends. From home to office, from toddlers to teenagers, every age group and every domain is covered for your convenience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Live Stream shopping can be considered as a bridge that covers the barrier between online shopping and brick-and-mortar retailing. We are familiar enough with the pros and cons of both ways of shopping. The live stream shopping just not covers the downsides of both trends but it is superior because of its own edges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stay tuned for more updates!</p>\r\n', 'Live stream shopping is much more than online shopping. Before going into any details, let’s have a brief look over what makes Live stream shopping more and more trendy?', '210210104301SG-What-Is-Live-Stream-Shopping.jpg', '2021-02-10 10:47:17', 'The-Future-of-E-commerce--2');
